Hey friends,

The members of The Provincial Archive are people just like you.  They download music and share with friends and don't feel guilty about it.  And they make a point of supporting independent artists and small labels.  They recognize that the free exchange of information is good for mankind.

That said, The Provincial Archive are not rich men.  At the time of this upload, they are in debt, and have yet to make any profits from music.  All they desire is to keep making records, and that costs a little money. If you like this recording, please consider supporting them by buying the album online or sending a donation via their website.  They promise not to waste your money on extravagance, but will instead spend it on making more music.  

And of course, please pass this on to your friends and keep seeding.  Word up.
